Package: NanoBAC
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of long read (Oxford Nanopore, PacBio) data from BAC or large plasmid sequencing
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pascal GP MARTIN
Maintainer: Pascal GP MARTIN <pgp.martin@gmail.com>
Description: Package of functions used to analyze long read data from BACs and other large plasmids
    This package is intended to be used in a pipeline developed for Oxford Nanopore sequencing
    of BACs containing ribosomal DNA.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
